  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the ability to occasionally sense the presence of the undead, whose existence is an insult to the natural cycle of life. As a Magic action, you can open your awareness to detect undead. Until the end of your next turn, you are able to see invisible undead and you know the location of any undead within 60 feet of you even through total cover, and that is not protected from Divination magic. This sense does not tell you anything about a creature's capabilities or identity.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
